observations.recommendation:
We recommend that management;
Strictly comply with the 7-day rule relative to the granting of cash advance for intelligence and confidential fund.
Directed the Municipal Accountant to record the liquidation within 5 days after the receipt of a copy of the transmittal of documents duly acknowledge by the ICFAU. He shall submit the corresponding JEV to the audit team. Ensure that the amount subject of Notice of Disallowance is restored upon receipt of the said notice from ICFAU.
